column6: doesn't appear broken, but is growing sideways with most of its foliage touching the ground.
had minor damage on bark of a shoot eminating from the basal shoot.  Mower came too close???
tree was broken (not totally snapped in two) at its basal stem.  Appears to have been from the most recent mowing (leaves are still green)
one of the large shoots eminating from the basal shoot is cracked in half and lying on the ground.  Possible damage from wind???
